name: FBuildPromotionImportWorkflowSettings
doc: Holds settings for the import workflow stage of the build promotion test

Diffuse: Import settings for the Diffuse texture
Normal: Import settings for the Normalmap texture
StaticMesh: Import settings for the static mesh
ReimportStaticMesh: Import settings for the static mesh to re-import
BlendShapeMesh: Import settings for the blend shape
MorphMesh: Import settings for the morph mesh
SkeletalMesh: Import settings for the skeletal mesh
Animation: Import settings for the animation asset.  (Will automatically use the skeleton of the skeletal mesh above)
SurroundSound: Import settings for the surround sound (Select any of the channels.  It will auto import the rest)
OtherAssetsToImport: Import settings for any other assets you may want to import
